column2: SELECT one, two FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN N.psf.i BETWEEN # AND # THEN # END one, CASE WHEN NN.psf.i BETWEEN # AND # THEN # END two FROM dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) as N INNER JOIN PhotoTag ON PhotoTag.objID = N.objID, dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) as NN INNER JOIN PhotoTag ON PhotoTag.objID = N.objID) PhotoTag
